e-mail: promed@usa.healthnet.org
[We need to beware of circular reasoning here. If fatal cases are being
discounted because they do not fit the picture of those associated with
HFMD or EV-71, then of course the epidemic will be ascribed to HFMD or
EV-71. But what did the other 8 cases die of, and why were they at first
thought to be part of the same outbreak? - Mod.JW
